WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.520
Hey, good morning family!

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:06.146
I am so excited to come on today and give you the word that the Lord has for you.

00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:10.635
I was praying and just asking, 'Lord, what do you have for your people today?

00:00:10.635 --> 00:00:19.786
' and He said, 'I want you to tell them this: for the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart who's perfect toward Him.

00:00:19.786 --> 00:00:25.936
' My message today is: How big, how bad is your 'want to'?

00:00:25.936 --> 00:00:27.080
You know what?

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:39.550
If you want to go do things for Jesus and you want to walk in the authority, the power, and the victory of the Lord, you've got to have a strong 'want to'.

00:00:39.550 --> 00:00:46.280
You've got to have a great desire to serve Him and a great yielded 'want to'.

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:53.560
There was one time when I was a little boy, I had warts all over my body.

00:01:05.074 --> 00:01:05.320
They were covering me from the top of my head, all over my chest, and all over my back.

00:01:07.145 --> 00:01:12.211
Every day I got made fun of at school because of those warts; they called me 'Wart Boy'.

00:01:13.394 --> 00:01:25.903
Every night I went home and, while getting ready for bed, I told my dad, 'I want you to anoint every single one of those warts with oil, and I'm believing I'm going to be healed.

00:01:25.903 --> 00:01:27.935
' I was just seven years old.

00:01:27.935 --> 00:01:41.975
Every night I would go in, and even sometimes when he would forget and go to bed, I would go in there: 'Daddy, you forgot to anoint my warts with oil because I believe that Jesus Christ was a healer.

00:01:41.975 --> 00:01:44.999
' He would say, 'Oh son, I'm tired.

00:01:44.999 --> 00:01:50.133
' I said, 'Dad, but you've got to!

00:01:50.133 --> 00:01:53.230
I believe I'm going to be healed.

00:02:00.986 --> 00:02:01.200
You've got to anoint these warts with oil.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:13.617
' So he anointed them, and this went on for probably close to a year, but my 'want to' was bigger than the pain of having those warts all over my body.

00:02:13.617 --> 00:02:16.160
My 'want to' being healed was great.

00:02:23.711 --> 00:02:24.008
So you've got to have a 'want to' that's stronger than what your circumstances are.

00:02:25.815 --> 00:02:30.840
It doesn't matter whatever is going on in your life or how big those circumstances may be.

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:43.062
You may look at it and think it's impossible, but if you have a 'want to' that's strong enough and a desire in your heart, God's going to come through for you.

00:02:43.062 --> 00:02:45.844
You've got to keep that 'want to' strong.

00:02:45.844 --> 00:02:54.292
That 'want to' was inside of me; it kept coming back and saying, 'Daddy, anoint those warts with oil, and Jesus is going to heal me.

00:02:54.292 --> 00:03:00.235
' Well, one morning I woke up and they were laying all beside me in my bed.

00:03:00.235 --> 00:03:03.644
All those warts had fallen off of my body.

00:03:03.644 --> 00:03:04.889
Glory to God!

00:03:04.889 --> 00:03:10.616
They all fell off my body and Jesus healed me in the middle of the night.

00:03:15.051 --> 00:03:16.407
I woke up the next day and was completely delivered from all those warts.

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:25.660
I ran in while my dad was still asleep in bed, grabbed a hold of his arm and said, 'Dad, look!

00:03:25.660 --> 00:03:28.480
Every one of the warts are gone!

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.008
' They were in piles in my bed.

00:03:31.008 --> 00:03:36.040
Jesus Christ healed me from the top of my head to the soles of my feet.

00:03:37.045 --> 00:03:53.736
I'm here to tell you, if you have a 'want to' in your heart that is strong enough that says, 'I will have what I say, I will have what I believe, and I'm going to confess that Jesus Christ is the healer,' He's a deliverer.

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:09.480
He is not a God who is a respecter of persons, and if He'll do it for me, He'll do it for you.

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:18.377
That's the kind of faith you've got to have—that bulldog faith that says, 'I'm not giving up; I'm going to keep on with my want to.

00:04:18.377 --> 00:04:24.984
' Blind Bartimaeus was at the gate and he was yelling, 'Jesus, Son of David, have mercy on me!

00:04:24.984 --> 00:04:29.000
